lead_paragraph: Jacksonville Jaguars Coach Jack Del Rio signed a five-year contract extension, a reward for winning his first playoff game. Del Rio’s salary was not disclosed, but it was believed to be a significant jump from the original five-year, $6.5 million contract he signed in 2003.
